dmca.title: TV DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
Original match 3 game created by Daniel
Cook of LostGarden; currently hosted on Facebook and Google+ and coming
soon to Android.

The clone cited in this form not only uses a name that is nearly identical
to our game's name (potentially causing confusion) but actually uses art in
the same style created by our artist! (We provide the art for free on our
website, but it is obviously not intended for people to clone our own games
with.)
